#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/observability-devservices-lgtm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Observability Dev Services with Grafana OTel LGTM"
msgstr "Dev Services de Observabilidade com Grafana OTel LGTM"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/observability-devservices-lgtm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This Dev Service provides the https://github.com/grafana/docker-otel-lgtm[Grafana OTel-LGTM], an `all-in-one` Docker image containing an https://opentelemetry.io/docs/collector[OpenTelemetry Collector] receiving and then forwarding telemetry data to Prometheus (metrics), Tempo (traces) and Loki (logs).\n"
"This data can then be visualized by https://github.com/grafana/grafana[Grafana]. The LGTM abbreviation stands for:"
msgstr "Este Dev Service fornece o https://github.com/grafana/docker-otel-lgtm[Grafana OTel-LGTM], uma imagem Docker `all-in-one` contendo um https://opentelemetry.io/docs/collector[OpenTelemetry Collector] que recebe e, em seguida, encaminha dados de telemetria para o Prometheus (métricas), Tempo (traces) e Loki (logs). \\nEstes dados podem então ser visualizados pelo https://github.com/grafana/grafana[Grafana]. A abreviação LGTM significa:"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/observability-devservices-lgtm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "L -> https://github.com/grafana/loki[Loki] (logs)"
msgstr "L -> https://github.com/grafana/loki[Loki] (logs)"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/observability-devservices-lgtm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "G -> https://github.com/grafana/grafana[Grafana] (metrics visualization)"
msgstr "G -> https://github.com/grafana/grafana[Grafana] (visualização de métricas)"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/observability-devservices-lgtm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "T -> https://github.com/grafana/tempo[Tempo] (traces)"
msgstr "T -> https://github.com/grafana/tempo[Tempo] (traces)"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/observability-devservices-lgtm.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "M -> https://grafana.com/oss/mimir[Mimir] (long term storage for Prometheus)"
msgstr "M -> https://grafana.com/oss/mimir[Mimir] (armazenamento de longo prazo para o Prometheus)"

